sections.text:
This class includes chanterelles that do not qualify for inclusion in the higher classes but satisfy the minimum requirements specified above. The following defects may be allowed, provided the chanterelles retain their essential characteristics as regards the quality, the keeping quality and presentation:
- superficial defects;
- defects in colouring;
- pest damage; and
- damage, including the removal of blemished parts.

